    {
      "id": "1l6kr4j7b",
      "questionNumber": 2,
      "questionText": "<p>Match List - I with List - II.</p>\n<p><style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-1wig{font-weight:bold;text-align:left;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-0lax{text-align:left;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n<table class=\"tg\" style=\"undefined;table-layout: fixed; width: 497px\">\n<colgroup>\n<col style=\"width: 53px\">\n<col style=\"width: 208px\">\n<col style=\"width: 40px\">\n<col style=\"width: 196px\">\n</colgroup>\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-1wig\"></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-1wig\">List - I<br>(Mixture)</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-1wig\"></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-1wig\">List - II<br>(Purification Process)</th>\n  </tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">(A)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Chloroform &amp; Aniline</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">(I)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Steam distillation</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">(B)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Benzoic acid &amp; Napthalene</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">(II)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Sublimation</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">(C)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Water &amp; Aniline</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">(III)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Distillation</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">(D)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Napthalene &amp; Sodium chloride</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">(IV)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0lax\">Crystallisation</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></p>\n<p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below :</p>",
